y anyway.PricingEarly Access Will Run $4.99 USUpon full completion the sale price will be raised.If this game does not yet satisfy you...making it cheaper won't fix that...making the game better will....so we will commit to that.I would say that likely someday down the road...we'd do a bundle...I mean...I like Christmas too! So That's It For Now.Let's Go Blow Some Stuff Up.Default Control SettingsKeyboard     Move: WASD/Arrow Keys    Toggle Autofire: F    Hover: Spacebar    Pause: Esc/PXBox Gamepad     Move: Joystick/D-Pad    Toggle Autofire: A/Y    Hover: B/X    Pause: StartPS3 Gamepad     Move: Joystick/D-Pad    Toggle Autofire: X/Triangle    Hover: Circle/Square    Pause: Start						
